body:
Is there a way I can mute myself? I almost got really overheated and flamed a couple of team mates in my last game and I really wanted to mute myself so I couldn't say anything else that might offend them.

 I know I can just not type anything but my stress is still there. When I get triggered, typing your anger out is kind of a way of relieving toxic stress and that might be a way for other people to relieve the stress too.

 So I was wondering if there is a way I can mute myself and if i get triggered and flame, i can type in chat but no one will see it... {{sticker:slayer-jinx-catface}}
